## Task 2 — Types of Logs

Common log categories you'll meet:

| Type | What it records |
|------|-----------------|
| **Application logs** | Events from a specific app (errors, transactions) |
| **Security logs** | Auth events, access control, policy changes |
| **System logs** | OS-level events (services, drivers, boot) |
| **Network logs** | Traffic, firewall allow/deny, connections |
| **Web server logs** | HTTP requests (access logs) and errors (error logs) |
| **Audit logs** | Who did what, when — accountability trail |

